# == Class: hadoop::pig
#
# Apache Pig is a platform for analyzing large data sets that consists of a
# high-level language for expressing data analysis programs, coupled with
# infrastructure for evaluating these programs
#
# === Parameters
#
# None
#
# === Variables
#
# None
#
# === Requires
#
# Java
# Hadoop
#
# === Sample Usage
#
# include hadoop-pig
#
